name: UnmodifiableMultiSetTest
description: Tests for the UnmodifiableMultiSet class, focusing on its unmodifiable behavior and factory methods.

test_cases.name: testAdd
test_cases.description: Tests that adding an element to an unmodifiable multiset throws an UnsupportedOperationException.

test_cases.name: testDecorateFactory
test_cases.description: Tests the factory method for creating an unmodifiable multiset and ensures it throws a NullPointerException when given null.

test_cases.name: testEntrySet
test_cases.description: Tests that the entry set of an unmodifiable multiset has the same size as the original multiset.

test_cases.name: testRemove
test_cases.description: Tests that removing an element from an unmodifiable multiset throws an UnsupportedOperationException.

test_cases.name: testSetCount
test_cases.description: Tests that setting the count of an element in an unmodifiable multiset throws an UnsupportedOperationException.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiable
test_cases.description: Tests that the objects created by the factory methods are instances of Unmodifiable.
